e UNP led regime of Dudley Senanayake. He upheld\nthe law and the constitution to the letter and won respect and admiration of all\npolitical parties.\n","linknr":283,"url":"William_Gopallawa","recorded":1375088043,"links":["/w/index.php?title=William_Gopallawa&action=edit","/w/index.php?title=William_Gopallawa&action=edit","//bits.wikimedia.org/favicon/wikipedia.ico","/w/opensearch_desc.php","//en.wikipedia.org/w/api.php?action=rsd","//creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/","/w/index.php?title=Special:RecentChanges&feed=atom","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=ext.gadget.DRN-wizard%2CReferenceTooltips%2Ccharinsert%2Cteahouse%7Cext.rtlcite%2Cwikihiero%7Cext.uls.nojs%7Cmediawiki.legacy.commonPrint%2Cshared%7Cmw.PopUpMediaTransform%7Cskins.vector&only=styles&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=site&only=styles&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=startup&only=scripts&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/geoiplookup","//meta.wikimedia.org","#mw-navigation","#p-search","/wiki/File:William_Gopallawa.JPG","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/fb/William_Gopallawa.JPG/220px-William_Gopallawa.JPG","/wiki/List_of_Presidents_of_Sri_Lanka","/wiki/President_of_Sri_Lanka","/wiki/Governor-General_of_Ceylon","/wiki/Junius_Richard_Jayewardene","/wiki/Governor-General_of_Ceylon","/wiki/Elizabeth_II","/wiki/Oliver_Ernest_Goonetilleke","/wiki/List_of_Presidents_of_Sri_Lanka","/wiki/Non-Aligned_Movement#Secretaries-General","/wiki/Houari_Boum%C3%A9dienne","/wiki/Junius_Richard_Jayawardene","/wiki/Matale","/wiki/British_Ceylon","/wiki/Sri_Lanka","/wiki/Colombo","/wiki/Sri_Lanka","/wiki/Nee","/wiki/Alma_mater","/wiki/St._Anthony%E2%80%99s_College,_Kandy","/wiki/Theravada_Buddhism","/wiki/Sinhala_language","/wiki/Tamil_language","/wiki/MBE","/wiki/Governor-General_of_Ceylon","/wiki/President_of_Sri_Lanka","/wiki/Republic","/wiki/Com